{"totalResults": 6, "vulnerabilities": [{"cve": {"id": "CVE-2013-4977", "sourceIdentifier": "cve@mitre.org", "published": "2014-03-03T16:55:04.037", "lastModified": "2025-04-12T10:46:40.837", "vulnStatus": "Deferred", "cveTags": [], "descriptions": [{"lang": "en", "value": "Buffer overflow in the RTSP Packet Handler in Hikvision DS-2CD7153-E IP camera with firmware 4.1.0 b130111 (Jan 2013), and possibly other devices, allows remote attackers to cause a denial of service (device crash and reboot) and possibly execute arbitrary code via a long string in the Range header field in an RTSP transaction."}, {"lang": "es", "value": "Desbordamiento de buffer en el manejador de paquetes RTSP en la c\u00e1mara Hikvision DS-2CD7153-E IP con firmware 4.1.0 b130111 (Jan 2013), y posiblemente otros dispositivos, permite a atacantes remotos causar una denegaci\u00f3n de servicio (ca\u00edda de dispositivo y reinicio) y posiblemente ejecutar c\u00f3digo arbitrario a trav\u00e9s de una cadena larga en el campo de cabecera Range en una transacci\u00f3n RTSP."}], "metrics": {"cvssMetricV2": [{"source": "nvd@nist.gov", "type": "Primary", "cvssData": {"version": "2.0", "vectorString": "AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C", "baseScore": 10.0, "accessVector": "NETWORK", "accessComplexity": "LOW", "authentication": "NONE", "confidentialityImpact": "COMPLETE", "integrityImpact": "COMPLETE", "availabilityImpact": "COMPLETE"}, "baseSeverity": "HIGH", "exploitabilityScore": 10.0, "impactScore": 10.0, "acInsufInfo": false, "obtainAllPrivilege": false, "obtainUserPrivilege": false, "obtainOtherPrivilege": false, "userInteractionRequired": false}]}, "weaknesses": [{"source": "nvd@nist.gov", "type": "Primary", "description": [{"lang": "en", "value": "CWE-119"}]}], "configurations": [{"operator": "AND", "nodes": [{"operator": "OR", "negate": false, "cpeMatch": [{"vulnerable": true, "criteria": "cpe:2.3:o:hikvision:ds-2cd7153-e_firmware:4.1.0_b130111:*:*:*:*:*:*:*", "matchCriteriaId": "F57E7BCA-5DA1-48D4-9496